                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3928" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0542</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8451 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购业绩承诺未实现，管理层何去何从</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">When Performance Commitments are not Fulfilled, What Management can Do?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">唐松莲，王振伟，张云莉，张琳倩，薛田田，于璐，余子健</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">佳电股份</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购；业绩承诺；管理层；未实现；佳电股份</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mergers and Acquisitions; Performance Commitment; Management; Unfulfilled; JEMC</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伴随着火爆并购重组和借壳，签订业绩承诺及其补偿协议公司日益增多，但2017年业绩承诺未达标比例达到24%。上市公司在欣欣向荣时刻签订高额业绩承诺，在行业低迷时面临经营困境，已成为公司在资产重组后的同质性问题。2010年，佳电股份借壳ST阿继上市，且基于未来盈利预测与ST阿继签订业绩承诺。谁曾想到，2011年佳电股份所处经营环境发生巨大变化，后续业绩承诺面临难以完成窘境。佳电股份董事长赵明和财务总监梁喜华等人在2013年董事会上一脸惆怅，如何处理行业衰落业绩承诺难以实现对公司影响，成为佳电股份董事会和管理层面临的难题。佳电股份董事会及管理层站在选择的十字路口上，是选择不作为还是作为？如果选择不作为，会有什么后果？如果选择作为，如何作为？是盈余管理、财务舞弊或重新签订业绩承诺？ </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Along with the mergers and acquisitions and backdoor&#160;listing, more and more&#160;companies&#160;have&#160;signed performance commitments and compensation agreements.&#160;However,&#160;the proportion of unfulfilled increased year by year&#160;and&#160;reached to 24%&#160;in 2017. That is to say, signing a high-performance commitment at the time of prosperity and prosperity, facing the operational dilemma in the downturn of the industry, has become a homogeneity problem after the company&#39;s asset restructuring. In 2010, JEMC listed on the back of ST Aji. Considering the&#160;future profitability forecast, JEMC&#160;signed a piece of performance commitments&#160;with ST Aji. Nobody could expect&#160;that the operating environment of JEMC. undergone tremendous changes in 2011&#160;which directly&#160;lead to the&#160;uncompleted&#160;of performance commitment signing before. Zhao Ming, the chairman of JEMC,&#160;Liang Xihua, the chief financial officer, and others fell into difficult circumstances. How to deal with&#160;it&#160;became the problem faced by JEMC&#39;s board of directors and management. The board of directors and management of JEMC. stood at the crossroads: Take actions or not? If we choose&#160;to ignore, what will happen? Can the company afford it? If we&#160;choose to act, what shall we do? Earnings management? Financial fraud? Or re-signing performance commitments?
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“并购重组”、 “业绩承诺”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
